President Gu,

294
00:12:45,479 --> 00:12:46,520
how is your health?

295
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,080
Have you been well lately?

296
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:54,799
Darn it, darn it, darn it.

297
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:55,919
I've completely lost my mind.

298
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,400
Darn it, darn it, darn it.

299
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:06,239
How did I become like this?

300
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,440
What did you say?

301
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,919
You didn't find anything?

302
00:13:12,599 --> 00:13:13,159
Yeah.

303
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:14,479
First, there are no bloodstains on the car.

304
00:13:14,479 --> 00:13:15,479
Second, there are no collision marks.

305
00:13:15,719 --> 00:13:16,799
And it hasn't been repaired recently.

306
00:13:17,559 --> 00:13:19,039
It means we have absolutely no evidence.

307
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:20,719
In other words,

308
00:13:20,719 --> 00:13:22,000
this car arrived at the scene,

309
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,760
but it didn't hit anyone.

310
00:13:23,119 --> 00:13:24,159
That's how it looks right now.

311
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:25,559
Senior,

312
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:27,159
do you think it's possible

313
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:28,479
that our initial investigation direction

314
00:13:28,479 --> 00:13:29,159
was wrong from the start?

315
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,400
Tan Feng isn't a murderer,

316
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,719
but the only eyewitness.

317
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:36,840
Even if he is an eyewitness,

318
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:38,280
what information can he provide now?

319
00:13:38,599 --> 00:13:40,479
Although we can't directly

320
00:13:40,479 --> 00:13:41,400
get any information from Tan Feng right now,

321
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,280
but do you remember when we caught him,

322
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:45,119
he said there was another mastermind?

323
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:46,440
Yes.

324
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,840
I've been thinking about this too.

325
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,440
It seems there must be

326
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,840
a bigger conspiracy behind this.

327
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,280
I think so too.

328
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:02,960
Take advantage of this personnel transfer

329
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,840
and go to the Japanese branch

330
00:14:05,239 --> 00:14:06,039
for a while.

331
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:08,200
If such a loss occurs again next time

332
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:10,919
and causes damage to the company,

333
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,280
I will have to consider

334
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,880
whether to give you another job opportunity.

335
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,039
It's me.

336
00:14:25,719 --> 00:14:27,239
Gu Rongchen is sending me to Japan.

337
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,599
I'm afraid I can't cooperate with you anymore.

338
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:32,159
I still have a lot of dirt on him.

339
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:33,520
I can give it all to you.

340
00:14:34,359 --> 00:14:35,000
Gu Rongchen.

341
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,599
What's his schedule like recently?

342
00:14:37,719 --> 00:14:39,159
You want to know his recent schedule?

343
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,320
Then what's my reward?

344
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,640
Do you want to go to Japan?

345
00:14:44,159 --> 00:14:45,200
Of course I don't want to go to Japan.

346
00:14:46,359 --> 00:14:46,960
Leave it to me.

347
00:14:47,280 --> 00:14:47,840
Okay.

348
00:15:00,239 --> 00:15:00,599
President Gu.

349
00:15:00,919 --> 00:15:01,599
And these.

350
00:15:01,599 --> 00:15:02,359
Please take a look.

351
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:02,960
Thank you.

352
00:15:03,039 --> 00:15:04,200
I already knew about this.

353
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,520
Hurry up and handle the accident.

354
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:06,640
We'll keep in touch by phone.

355
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,320
Hello, let me go over the schedule with you.

356
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:11,960
President Gu.

357
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,719
We have a little situation.

358
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:13,320
What's wrong?

359
00:15:13,479 --> 00:15:14,760
The stylist's car...

360
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:15,679
was in a multi-car pileup.

361
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:16,440
Is he okay?

362
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:17,320
Don't worry, he's fine.

363
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,520
But today,

364
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,679
he probably won't be able to make it.

365
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:21,760
He can't make it?

366
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:22,679
What about me?

367
00:15:23,359 --> 00:15:24,119
Don't worry.

368
00:15:24,119 --> 00:15:24,840
I know for this interview,

369
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,679
you definitely need styling.

370
00:15:25,799 --> 00:15:26,440
So I...

371
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:27,880
Excuse me.

372
00:15:28,559 --> 00:15:29,159
Sorry.

373
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:29,719
I'm late.

374
00:15:30,479 --> 00:15:30,960
Do you think this will work?

375
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:31,599
No problem, no problem.

376
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,400
So,

377
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,840
I had Lin Jiaqi prepare a few suits.

378
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:34,919
And while she's at it,

379
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:35,799
she can do your styling.

380
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:38,640
Are you kidding me?

381
00:15:39,119 --> 00:15:40,119
How could I be kidding, President Gu?

382
00:15:40,119 --> 00:15:41,080
It's our only option right now.

383
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,000
Oh right, Secretary Lin.

384
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,719
You're okay with matching suits, right?

385
00:15:43,719 --> 00:15:44,559
You know how to tie a tie, right?

386
00:15:44,559 --> 00:15:45,320
You know how to do styling, right?

387
00:15:45,559 --> 00:15:46,039
It has to be you.

388
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:46,960
No problem at all.

389
00:15:47,119 --> 00:15:48,000
So I'll leave it to you.

390
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,799
Really, thanks for your hard work.

391
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:49,880
I still have things to do.

392
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:50,960
I need to handle the accident situation.

393
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:51,880
Bye-bye.

394
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:52,280
Qi! Qi!

395
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,679
Do your best! Thanks, thanks a lot!

396
00:16:05,039 --> 00:16:05,520
Let's begin.

397
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:06,520
I...

398
00:16:11,599 --> 00:16:12,320
Let me see.

399
00:16:20,719 --> 00:16:21,400
Close your eyes.

400
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,479
I only know how to do my own makeup.

401
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:27,359
I've never done makeup for a man before.

402
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,679
And I've never had my makeup done by a girl.

403
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:31,359
Close your eyes.

404
00:16:35,799 --> 00:16:36,320
What are you doing?

405
00:16:37,559 --> 00:16:38,239
Drawing your eyebrows.

406
00:16:51,599 --> 00:16:52,159
Done.

407
00:16:52,239 --> 00:16:52,880
Let me see.
